  "instructions": [
    "Combine chicken, mixture powder, ginger, garlic in a bowl and mix well.",
    "Refrigerate the mixture for at least 30 minutes to allow the flavors to meld.",
    "Bring a large pot of chicken broth and water to a boil, then reduce the heat to a simmer.",
    "Add wonton wrappers to the pot and cook for 2-3 minutes or until they float to the surface.",
    "Transfer the cooked wontons to a plate, then ladle the hot broth over them.",
    "Sprinkle green onions over the top of the wontons and serve hot.",
    "Season with soy sauce, sesame oil, and salt to taste.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
